# Calourie AI — Server-Side Backend + Admin Dashboard Guide

> **Concept**: Room stays on mobile. The backend is a **middleware API gateway** that proxies all external API calls (OpenFoodFacts, Gemini, etc.). The **Web Dashboard is an Admin Panel** to manage APIs, keys, providers, and monitor usage — all without pushing app updates.

