### What Changes vs What Stays

| Aspect | Current | New |
|--------|---------|-----|
| **Room (local DB)** | ✅ Stays | ✅ No change |
| **UI (Compose)** | ✅ Stays | ✅ No change |
| **ViewModels / UseCases** | ✅ Stays | ✅ No change |
| **API base URL** | Hardcoded `openfoodfacts.org` | Points to **your server** |
| **API keys** | Hardcoded in app (or none) | Stored on server, managed by admin |
| **Which API to call** | Only OpenFoodFacts | Server decides (configurable from admin) |
| **Gemini / AI models** | Would require app update to change | Change from admin panel instantly |
| **User analytics** | None | Server tracks all requests |
| **Load balancing** | None | Server distributes across providers |

