### Backend Response Format

Your server must return data in the **same format** as OpenFoodFacts so the existing [ProductResponseDto](file:///e:/Desktop/calourie_ai/app/src/main/java/com/example/calorieapp/data/DataSource/remote/dto/ProductDto.kt#28-35) and [ProductDto](file:///e:/Desktop/calourie_ai/app/src/main/java/com/example/calorieapp/data/DataSource/remote/dto/ProductDto.kt#5-27) parsers still work:

```json
{
    "status": 1,
    "product": {
        "product_name": "Milk",
        "brands": "Nestle",
        "image_url": "https://...",
        "nutriments": {
            "energy-kcal_100g": 42,
